<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.10.4">
<l>piṟaiyi ṉoḷiyeyiṟi lakamuṟuki yetirporutu meṉavanta vacurar</l>
<l>iṟaikaḷ vaineṟune ṟeṉaveṟiya vavarvayiṟa ḻalaniṉṟa perumāṉ</l>
<l>ciṟaikoḷ mayilkuyilpa yilamalarka ḷukavaḷimu ralavaṭikoḷ neṭumā</l>
<l>naṟaicey poḻilmaḻaita vaḻumnanti puraviṇṇa karamnaṇṇu maṉamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O heart, go to Nantipura Viṇṇakaram where mist creeps</l>
<l rend="indent">through groves made fragrant</l>
<l>By tall mangos with [massive] roots, as beetles chirp, as blossoms scatter,</l>
<l rend="indent">and as feathered peacocks and coocoos cry,</l>
<l>[The city of] the great lord who endured when he smashed,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a grinding [sound], the joints of the demons,</l>
<l rend="indent">so their stomachs burned,</l>
<l>Which had come, as their fangs gleamed with the light of a crescent moon,</l>
<l rend="indent">when they said “We will fight against [you]!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
